as/c36e628a5e8f7725e367e4472d2aac37.webm?t=1739514816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/828570/extras/c36e628a5e8f7725e367e4472d2aac37.mp4?t=1739514816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与隐藏的角色建立关系，帮助他们完成任务，与他们进行交易，并了解你的旅程的重要信息。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >找到并对抗疯狂法师瓦蒂。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/828570/extras/6219ed4361363a2989f4ec6946c1ccf5.poster.avif?t=1739514816\" width=616 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/828570/extras/6219ed4361363a2989f4ec6946c1ccf5.webm?t=1739514816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/828570/extras/6219ed4361363a2989f4ec6946c1ccf5.mp4?t=1739514816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索地图的每个角落，解锁疯狂法师的隐藏领域。如果你获得了足够的资源、遗物和游戏世界的知识，你就可以击败他并最终逃离这个水晶监狱。</p>",
